---
title: Pork and Chinese Eggplant Stir-Fry over Brown Rice
description: Chinese eggplant is longer and thinner-skinned than its Italian cousin, making it perfect for stir-frying. Sautéed with yellow squash, pork, and an umami-packed sauce, this stir-fry hits all the marks. Brown rice is a healthy swap we prefer for its heartiness.
